title: Blazing 5 - Week 10
itunes:title: Blazing 5 - Week 10
description:
Colin goes over his Blazing 5 picks with Steve Fezzik of Pregame.com and Fox Sports Radio who tells him which games the wise guys in Vegas agree or disagree with. Here are the games Colin and Steve go over in week 10:


Giants @ Jets

Cardinals @ Buccaneers

Panthers @ Packers

Rams @ Steelers

Seahawks @ 49ers


Plus, Colin reveals a 6th bonus pick exclusive to this podcast.
